            <title>[SOLR-7385] The clusterstatus API does not return the config name for a collection</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-7385</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The config name used while creating the collection is not returned by the &apos;clusterstatus&apos; API. I propose to return the configset name used by a collection keyed by &quot;configName&quot; as part of the collection information.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
